The '''Vaj Desert''' was one of several [[Desert/Legends|deserts]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ingo/Legends|Ingo]]. When the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Zevel Hortine]] dropped [[Gender/Legends|his]] cargo to avoid prosecution by the authorities, much of it landed in the Vaj Desert, including the [[Droid/Legends|droids]] [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] and [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]]. It was here that the droids met the [[Landspeeder/Legends|speeder]] racers, [[Thall Joben/Legends|Thall Joben]] and [[Jord Dusat]], who were using the desert to race in.

